srcstlsupportincludedir)" "$(DESTDIR)$(eigensrcsuperlusupportincludedir)" "$(DESTDIR)$(eigensrcsvdincludedir)" "$(DESTDIR)$(eigensrcumfpacksupportincludedir)" "$(DESTDIR)$(eigenunsupportedincludedir)" "$(DESTDIR)$(eigenunsupportedsrcincludedir)" "$(DESTDIR)$(fmtincludedir)" "$(DESTDIR)$(hpcombiincludedir)" "$(DESTDIR)$(hpcombisimdearmincludedir)" "$(DESTDIR)$(hpcombisimdemipsincludedir)" "$(DESTDIR)$(hpcombisimdewasmincludedir)" "$(DESTDIR)$(hpcombisimdex86includedir)" "$(DESTDIR)$(magicenumincludedir)" "$(DESTDIR)$(pkgincludedir)" "$(DESTDIR)$(rxrangesincludedir)"; do \
	  test -z "$$dir" || $(MKDIR_P) "$$dir"; \
	done
